Package com.oracle.coherence.grpc

Low-level utilities for Coherence gRPC server and client implementation.
Since:
20.06
Author:
Jonathan Knight 2019.11.07
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryHelper
    A helper class of methods to convert between Binary instances and proto-buffer byte values.
    CacheRequestHolder<Req,​Res>
    A class that holds a gRPC request, an associated NamedCache and Binary converters.
    CacheRequestHolder.DownConverter
    A Converter that converts from a Binary serialized in one format to a Binary key serialized in a different format.
    CacheRequestHolder.UpConverter
    A Converter that converts from a Binary serialized in one format to a Binary serialized in a different format.
    CredentialsHelper
    A helper class to resolve gRPC credentials.
    PofMarshaller<T>
    gRPC Marshaller that uses POF for serialization.
    PofMarshaller.Supplier
    A MarshallerSupplier implementation that supplies instance of a default PofMarshaller.
    Requests
    A factory to simplify creating proto-buffer requests.
    SafeStreamObserver<T>
    A StreamObserver that handles exceptions correctly.
    SerializerMarshaller<T>
    gRPC Marshaller implementation that delegates to the specified Serializer.
    SerializerMarshaller.Supplier
    A MarshallerSupplier implementation that supplies instance of a default ExternalizableLite serializer.
    SimpleDaemonPoolExecutor
    An Executor that uses a DaemonPool to execute tasks.
